lead_paragraph: Dillon Brooks had 30 points and nine assists, both career highs, to lead No. 16 Oregon to a 76-66 victory over Utah on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Brooks Scores 30 as No. 16 Oregon Beats Utah 76-66
